@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home | About";
}

<section class="about_us_section">
    <div class="about_us_left_container">
        <img src="/photo/images/bus_park_together.png" alt="Our Company Location" class="about_us_image" />
    </div>
    <div class="about_us_right_container">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to JMBus, where we are committed to providing top-notch transportation services with a focus on customer satisfaction.
            <br><br>
            Established in 2000, we have continually expanded our fleet and services to meet the growing demands of our customers. Our mission is to offer safe, efficient, and comfortable travel options to all our passengers.
            <br><br>
            With a well-maintained fleet and experienced drivers, we ensure that every journey with us is a pleasant one.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="services_section">
    <h2 class="services_title">
        <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Our Services
    </h2>
    <div class="service_card">
        <i class="fas fa-bus service_icon"></i>
        <h3>Bus Rental</h3>
        <p>We offer a wide range of bus options.Ideal for university group trips, corporate events, and personal travel.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service_card">
        <i class="fas fa-bus service_icon"></i>
        <h3>Bus Schedule</h3>
        <p>We provide real-time bus schedules for all our routes, ensuring you never miss a ride.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service_card">
        <i class="fas fa-cogs service_icon"></i>
        <h3>Maintenance Service</h3>
        <p>Our fleet is regularly maintained to ensure safety, comfort, and reliability. We also offer on-demand service and repair options.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service_card">
        <i class="fas fa-user-tie service_icon"></i>
        <h3>Corporate Travel</h3>
        <p>We cater to business needs with customized travel solutions for corporate events, conferences, and meetings.</p>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="team_section">
    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <div class="team_member">
        <img src="/photo/images/founder.jpg" alt="Founder" class="team_img" />
        <h3>Our Founder - Kong Yih Hern</h3>
        <p>With over 20 years in the transportation industry, Dato Kong established JMBus to make travel more comfortable and efficient for all.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="team_member">
        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/5.jpg" alt="CEO" class="team_img" />
        <h3>CEO - Michael Johnson</h3>
        <p>The CEO leads JMBus with a vision to revolutionize the transportation industry by implementing new technologies and sustainable practices.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="team_member">
        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/3.jpg" alt="Bus In-Charge Executive" class="team_img" />
        <h3>Bus Executive - Sarah Lee</h3>
        <p>Our Bus In-Charge Executive ensures all our buses are operating smoothly, coordinating drivers and managing the fleet for optimal performance.</p>
    </div>
</section>


